          </li>
          <li class="next" data-controls="next" aria-controls="customize" tabindex="-1">
              <i class="fas fa-angle-right"></i>
          </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="my-slider">
          <div class="slider-item">
              <div class="slider-card">
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4">
                    <div class="slider-card-agent">
                      <div class="agent-name">Alex Dummat</div>
                      <div class="agent-agency">Montecristo Travel</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8">
                    <div class="slider-card-testimonial">
                      My clients Mr and Mrs Dantes were very happy with their transfer. Thank you for an impeccable service, as always.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
          </div>

          <div class="slider-item">
              <div class="slider-card">
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4">
                    <div class="slider-card-agent">
                      <div class="agent-name">John Ronald Tolcane</div>
                      <div class="agent-agency">Ringo Travel</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8">
                    <div class="slider-card-testimonial">
                      I love booking with My Private Transfer. I can keep track easily of my commissions and got great feedback from my clients Mr and Mrs Baggins, for their round-trip to Normandy. My client had even lost a precious ring in the car, which was brought back later to the hotel.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
          </div>

          <div class="slider-item">
              <div class="slider-card">
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4">
                    <div class="slider-card-agent">
                      <div class="agent-name">Jules Vernon</div>
                      <div class="agent-agency">80 days Travel</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8">
                    <div class="slider-card-testimonial">
                      I booked a last-minute transfer for my client Mr Fog, who was very happy with the comfort of the car.
                    </div>
